visual_events.description: The FPV drone takes off from the ground, approaching a large abandoned structure.
The drone ascends rapidly, flying over the top of the structure, revealing the ocean view behind it.
The drone dives vertically, showcasing the structure from above, then flies through an opening.
The drone performs a quick spin, showing the surrounding environment of the abandoned park.
The drone flies low to the ground, gliding over colorful painted patterns on the pavement.
The drone navigates through a dark, covered passageway adorned with graffiti.
The drone flies through a narrow archway into another section of the abandoned building.
The drone continues through the darker interior, showcasing more graffiti-covered walls.
The drone emerges from the darkness into a brighter, open courtyard with trees.
The drone dives down a stairwell, entering a lower level of the structure.
The drone explores the dark, subterranean tunnels beneath the structure.
The drone ascends from the underground, back into the main courtyard area.
The drone flies rapidly towards the large, skeletal main structure again.
The drone performs a complex maneuver, flying over the top of the structure while showcasing the ocean.
The drone descends into the heart of the main building, revealing a large graffiti eye on the back wall.
The drone flies through a decorated archway within the main structure.
The drone flies upwards along the exterior wall of the structure.
The drone executes a dive into a small opening on a concrete platform.
The drone navigates through a dense, overgrown area with trees and remnants of buildings.
The drone flies through a window opening into a room, then quickly exits.
The drone approaches the main entrance of the large structure, flying up the stairs.
The drone flies through the interior of the main structure, showcasing the open ceiling and graffiti.
The drone ascends above the structure, offering a panoramic view of the beach and surroundings.
The drone performs an inverted flight high above the complex, capturing a wide aerial view.
The drone descends back into the main structure's central area.
The drone flies very close to the large graffiti eye, then ascends straight up through the skeletal roof.
The drone flies over the top of the structure, performing a spin, and nearly crashes.
The drone recovers from the close call and returns to the ground level.
The drone flies into the entrance of the main structure and then through its interior.
The drone flies out of the main structure, showcasing its speed and agility.
The drone performs a quick dive and pull-up maneuver around a blue barrel.
The drone flies back towards the main entrance of the structure.
The drone re-enters the main hall of the building.
The drone flies up and over the structure, showcasing the coastal view.
The drone executes an inverted turn, providing an aerial perspective of the entire abandoned complex.
The drone descends back into the structure's interior.
The drone exits the main hall into a tree-lined pathway.
The drone performs another dive into a dark, lower-level opening.
The drone emerges from the dark opening and flies past old structures.
The drone flies towards and through another small building entrance.
The drone exits the building and maneuvers around obstacles.
The drone approaches the large structure and performs an acrobatic ascent over it.
The drone performs a dizzying, fast dive into the structure's interior.
The drone flies through the interior, showcasing the graffiti art and structural elements.
The drone exits the structure and flies high, performing a complex 360-degree roll above it.
The drone dives down into the structure, close to the prominent eye graffiti.
The drone flies straight up from the eye graffiti, shooting towards the open sky.
The drone flies out of the structure, makes a sharp turn, narrowly avoiding a collision.
The drone recovers and flies over a wooded area.
The drone approaches the main structure and flies into its entrance.
The drone flies through the interior of the main structure, then exits it.
The drone flies low across the ground, passing by a circular fountain area.
The drone flies through a covered entrance, passing under trees and structures.
The drone lands softly on the paved ground.
